<div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Main article=
: <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gaussian_elimination" title=3D"G=
aussian elimination">Gaussian elimination</a></div>
<p>A common approach to finding the rank of a matrix is to reduce it to a s=
impler form, generally <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Row_echelon=
