number" title=3D"Real number">real numbers</a> whose row rank is <span clas=
s=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">r</span>. Therefore, the di=
mension of the row space of <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-styl=
e:italic;">A</span> is <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:ita=
lic;">r</span>.  Let <span class=3D"texhtml"><b>x</b><sub>1</sub>, <b>x</b>=
<sub>2</sub>, ..., <b>x</b><sub><i>r</i></sub></span> be a <a href=3D"https=
