a)">kernel</a> of <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;"=
>f</span>.  The <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rank%E2%80%93nulli=
ty_theorem" title=3D"Rank=E2=80=93nullity theorem">rank=E2=80=93nullity the=
orem</a> states that this definition is equivalent to the preceding one.
</p>
